From a8e3ae8098adfea079ac3fc8cb73abaf636ba2ec Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 17:27:23 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: button mapping, screenshot upload, and game profiles
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Three bug fixes:

BUG 1: A/X/Y/B/R1/L1/R2/L2 not detected, D-pad detected as R2/L2
Root cause: GamepadPlugin sent axis array as [axisX, axisY, axisZ,
axisRZ, hatX, hatY] but hatX/hatY (D-pad) were in position [4][5]
which GamepadTester expected to be L2/R2 triggers.

Fix: Read AXIS_BRAKE (L2) and AXIS_GAS (R2) properly. Array is now
[axisX, axisY, axisZ, axisRZ, l2Trigger, r2Trigger]. D-pad (HAT axis)
is now emitted as button events (DPAD_UP/DOWN/LEFT/RIGHT) instead of
axis values — matches how Android gamepad D-pad actually works.

BUG 2: Screenshot upload not displaying
Root cause: OverlayCanvas used 'background' shorthand which doesn't
work with CSS gradient strings (only works with backgroundImage).
Fix: Changed back to 'backgroundImage' + 'backgroundSize: cover' +
'backgroundPosition: center'. Both gradient (preset) and blob: URL
(custom upload) work correctly with backgroundImage.

BUG 3: Game profiles too few (only 1 Genshin)
Root cause: INITIAL_PROFILES only had 1 profile (Genshin with 2 buttons).
Fix: Expanded to 5 game profiles with full button layouts:
- Genshin Impact (10 buttons: A/X/Y/B/RT/LT/START/SELECT + 2 sticks)
- PUBG Mobile (10 buttons: RT/LT/B/X/A/Y/START/SELECT + 2 sticks)
- Mobile Legends (7 buttons: A/X/Y/B/START/SELECT + 1 stick)
- COD Mobile (10 buttons: RT/LT/B/X/A/Y/LB/RB + 2 sticks)
- Free Fire (8 buttons: RT/LT/B/A/Y/X + 2 sticks)
